The Coding Introduction Course by 4Geeks Academy is a program designed to teach the basics of web development, including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It is an online course with a duration of 9 weeks. No previous coding skills are required, and the course is available in English and Spanish. Students will learn through practical projects and hands-on experience. By the end of the course, students will be able to build interactive and responsive websites. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/coding-introduction. stop